# Project Overview

This library provides Haskell bindings to the OpenAI API using the Servant framework. It offers a type-safe interface for interacting with various OpenAI endpoints.

## Main Components

- [src/OpenAI/V1.hs](mdc:src/OpenAI/V1.hs) - Main entry point for the library, exports the Methods record and utility functions
- [openai-example/Main.hs](mdc:openai-example/Main.hs) - Example application demonstrating basic usage

## Project Structure

- `src/OpenAI/V1/` - Contains modules for each OpenAI API endpoint
- `openai-example/` - Example application showing library usage
- `tasty/` - Test suite

## Key Features

- Type-safe API with proper Haskell data types
- Support for all OpenAI API endpoints
- Convenient helper functions for authentication and environment setup
